{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-template-js","path":"/pages/about/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"e4f25623-830e-5fa7-8336-50039837fe0b","html":"<h2 id=\"저는\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%80%EB%8A%94\" aria-label=\"저는 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>저는!</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">아름다운 코드를 추구하고, 배움과 소통을 사랑해요!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">명확한 변수명, 역할이 뚜렷하고 동작이 확실한 함수를 좋아해요!\n\n공부하며 모르던 것에 대한 지식을 충전하는 느낌,\n대화를 통해 사고력이 단단해지는 느낌이 너무 좋아요!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"빠른-것보다-바른-것이-좋아요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B9%A0%EB%A5%B8-%EA%B2%83%EB%B3%B4%EB%8B%A4-%EB%B0%94%EB%A5%B8-%EA%B2%83%EC%9D%B4-%EC%A2%8B%EC%95%84%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"빠른 것보다 바른 것이 좋아요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>빠른 것보다, 바른 것이 좋아요!</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">빠르게 하는것도 좋지만,\n\n올바르게 하는것을 더 좋아해요!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"재미있게-개발하고-싶어요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9E%AC%EB%AF%B8%EC%9E%88%EA%B2%8C-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0-%EC%8B%B6%EC%96%B4%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"재미있게 개발하고 싶어요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>재미있게 개발하고 싶어요!</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">함께하는 사람들과 즐겁게 소통하고 싶고,\n\n사적인 영역이나 민감한 부분에 대해서는 서로 배려하며\n\n즐겁고, 행복한 시간을 보내고 싶어요!</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"About mango","date":null,"description":null,"socialImage":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/pages/about/"}}}